column8: Partly cloudy. The chance of early fog . Medium (50%) chance of showers, falling as snow above 1500 metres. Winds southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light in the late evening. Daytime maximum temperatures between 12 and 17.

Partly cloudy. The chance of fog in the early morning. Medium (50%) chance of light showers in the southwest, slight (20%) chance elsewhere. Light winds becoming west to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the morning then becoming light in the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 3 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching between 14 and 18.

Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog. Light winds becoming east to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 3 and 7 with daytime temperatures reaching between 16 and 20.

Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog. Slight (30%) chance of a shower in the afternoon and evening. Light winds becoming south to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day then becoming light during the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 5 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching between 17 and 22.
